            453,
            814
          ],
          "block_id": 0,
          "block_order": 1
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "被子植物与我们的生活息息相关，我们日常生活中的衣、食、住、行，往往都离不开它们。例如，制造汽车和自行车轮胎的原料就来自橡胶树。许多中药材也来自被子植物，如人参、枸杞、杜仲、黄连、甘草等。关于被子植物与我们日常生活的关系，你还能举出哪些更为重要的例子呢？",
          "block_bbox": [
            806,
            205,
            2066,
            681
          ],
          "block_id": 1,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "比较",
          "block_bbox": [
            1049,
            880,
            1161,
            937
          ],
          "block_id": 2,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "",
          "block_bbox": [
            208,
            1006,
            740,
            1566
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "figure_title",
          "block_content": "白网纹草（双子叶植物）",
          "block_bbox": [
            351,
            1611,
            619,
            1720
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "叶片上粗细不等的脉络叫叶脉。请仔细观察左右两图中的植物，比较它们的叶脉，说说这两者之间有什么区别。",
          "block_bbox": [
            791,
            1048,
            1409,
            1447
          ],
          "block_id": 5,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "练习",
          "block_bbox": [
            1118,
            1944,
            1229,
            1998
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "",
          "block_bbox": [
            1465,
            1024,
            2022,
            1639
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "figure_title",
          "block_content": "银线乌巢凤梨（单子叶植物）",
          "block_bbox": [
            1607,
            1605,
            1887,
            1716
          ],
          "block_id": 8,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "1.判断下列说法是否正确。正确的画“√”，错误的画“×\"",
          "block_bbox": [
            171,
            2080,
            1692,
            2133
          ],
          "block_id": 9,
          "block_order": 6
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "（1）松的球果不是果实。",
          "block_bbox": [
            235,
            2166,
            823,
            2216
          ],
          "block_id": 10,
          "block_order": 7
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "（2）裸子植物和被子植物的种子中都有胚。8",
          "block_bbox": [
            236,
            2246,
            2030,
            2298
          ],
          "block_id": 11,
          "block_order": 8
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "（3）裸子植物的种子比被子植物的种子能得到更好的保护。",
          "block_bbox": [
            240,
            2326,
            1642,
            2377
          ],
          "block_id": 12,
          "block_order": 9
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "2.将种子的结构与其相应的功能用线连接起来。",
          "block_bbox": [
            169,
            2406,
            1296,
            2456
          ],
          "block_id": 13,
          "block_order": 10
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "种皮储藏养料\n胚保护胚\n胚乳能发育成新植株\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            341,
            2486,
            1380,
            2698
          ],
          "block_id": 14,
          "block_order": 11
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "3.被子植物具有哪些特点，使它们成为地球上分布最广泛的植物类群?",
          "block_bbox": [
            171,
            2724,
            1856,
            2782
          ],
          "block_id": 15,
          "block_order": 12
        },
        {
          "block_label": "number",
